IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. PRIMES.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 LIMIT PIC 9(4) VALUE 30.
01 CANDIDATE PIC 9(4) VALUE 2.
01 DIVISOR PIC 9(4) VALUE 0.
01 IS-PRIME PIC 9 VALUE 0.
01 PRIME-COUNT PIC 9(4) VALUE 0.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
DISPLAY "PRIMES UP TO 30".
PERFORM UNTIL CANDIDATE > LIMIT
    MOVE 1 TO IS-PRIME
    MOVE 2 TO DIVISOR
    PERFORM UNTIL DIVISOR * DIVISOR > CANDIDATE
        IF CANDIDATE MOD DIVISOR = 0
            MOVE 0 TO IS-PRIME
            COMPUTE DIVISOR = CANDIDATE
        END-IF
        ADD 1 TO DIVISOR
    END-PERFORM
    IF IS-PRIME = 1
        DISPLAY "PRIME" CANDIDATE
        ADD 1 TO PRIME-COUNT
    END-IF
    ADD 1 TO CANDIDATE
END-PERFORM
DISPLAY "TOTAL" PRIME-COUNT.
STOP RUN.
